To apply the patch:

Download NOMAD from http://www.gerad.ca/NOMAD (Cycle 6)

Unpack NOMAD

Change directory to the NOMAD directory 

Run the command "patch -p1 <NOMADPATCHLOCATION/NOMAD.Neurofitter-0.9.1.patch
(where NOMADPATCHLOCATION is the directory containing the patch)


To compile NOMAD:

Run the following commands in the NOMAD directory:
make -f Lib_Makefile_parallel


Now you can adapt the Makefile of Neurofitter so that it points to the directory containing NOMAD


